## SPECS SECTIONS

### F-04 · Footer
Fichiers : sections/footer.liquid, assets/section-footer.css, snippets/country-selector.liquid
Settings :
- logo (image_picker) + logo_width (range 60-200, default 100)
- color_scheme (default scheme-3 dark)
- show_payment_icons (checkbox, default true)
- show_country_selector + show_language_selector (checkboxes)
- footer_text (richtext)
Blocks (max 4) : menu (heading+link_list), text (heading+richtext), newsletter (heading+subtext)
Requirements : country selector via {% form 'localization' %}, payment icons via {{ shop.enabled_payment_types }}
Social links settings : instagram_url, facebook_url, tiktok_url, pinterest_url, youtube_url
Layout : 4 col desktop / 2 col tablette / 1 col mobile

### F-05 · Announcement bar
Fichier : sections/announcement-bar.liquid
Settings : color_scheme, auto_rotate (default true), rotation_speed (3-10s, default 5), show_close_button
Blocks (max 5) : announcement : text + link (url)
Comportement : rotation auto, transition slide ou fade, cookie si fermeture

### F-06 · Snippets globaux
image.liquid : params image/widths/sizes/class/alt/loading/fetchpriority — focal point + srcset + lazy default
price.liquid : product/use_variant/show_badges — prix barré + actuel + SALE/SOLD OUT + selling plans + Shop Pay Installments
global.js : trapFocus/removeTrapFocus, onKeyUpEscape, debounce/throttle, fetchConfig, PubSub, QuantityInput custom element, aria-live regions

### H-01 · Hero
Fichier : sections/hero.liquid
Settings :
- media_type : image | video | slideshow (default image)
- image + image_mobile (image_picker, focal point)
- video_url (url Vimeo/YouTube) + video_file (video Shopify)
- overlay_opacity (range 0-80 step 5, default 20)
- color_scheme (default scheme-3)
- height : full(100vh) | large(80vh) | medium(60vh) | small(40vh)
- text_position : top-left/center/right | center | bottom-left/center/right (default bottom-center)
- subheading (11px uppercase, AU-DESSUS heading) + heading + button_label/url/style
- autoplay (video, default true) + show_scroll_indicator
Blocks : slide (si slideshow) — image+heading+subheading+button, max 5, crossfade ou slide, duration 3-8s
Comportement : vidéo autoplay muted loop playsinline — reduced-motion = poster image
Scroll indicator : chevron animé, disparaît au scroll

### H-02 · Featured collection + card-product
Fichier : sections/featured-collection.liquid + snippets/card-product.liquid
Settings :
- heading + subheading, collection, products_to_show (4-12, default 8)
- columns_desktop (3|4|5, default 4), columns_mobile (1|2, default 2)
- show_view_all + view_all_label
- card_style : standard | minimal | editorial (default standard)
- color_scheme, image_ratio : portrait|square|landscape (default portrait)
- show_secondary_image (hover swap, default true)
- show_vendor, show_rating
card-product.liquid requis : image principale + secondaire hover swap, focal point, badges SALE/SOLD OUT/NEW, price barré, quick add (+/variant picker), wishlist localStorage, lazy loading sauf 1ère card

### H-03 · Editorial banner
Settings : layout (image-right|image-left|image-full), image+focal, image_ratio, color_scheme
subheading+heading+text(richtext)+button, image_overlay_opacity
Blocks : feature : icon(select)+text

### H-04 · Marquee
Settings : color_scheme, speed (20-120s, default 40), pause_on_hover, separator (bullet|dash|star|diamond)
Blocks : text (text) — répété en boucle infinie
CSS animation marquee linear infinite — reduced-motion: animation-play-state:paused

### H-05 · Lookbook / Shop the look
Settings : heading+subheading, color_scheme, layout (single|split)
Blocks (max 3) : look : image+focal, jusqu'à 4 produits, hotspot_x/y_1..4 (range 0-100)
Comportement : bouton + positionné via left:X% top:Y%, click = popover image+titre+prix+ATC
Mobile : scroll horizontal

### H-06 · Testimonials
Settings : heading+subheading, color_scheme, layout (grid|carousel), columns_desktop (2|3), show_rating
Blocks : testimonial : rating(1-5)+text(richtext)+author+author_title+author_image

### H-07 · Newsletter
Settings : color_scheme (default scheme-3), heading+subtext, button_label, show_name_field, disclaimer
Form : {% form 'customer' %} avec contact[tags]:'newsletter'
Success state inline (pas de reload), validation email inline

### H-08 · Press / Logos
Settings : heading, color_scheme, layout (logos|quotes)
Blocks (max 8) : logo : image+url+quote
logos = grille niveaux de gris hover couleur / quotes = carousel

### H-09 · Countdown
Settings : heading, target_date (ISO 8601), color_scheme, show_labels, after_end (hide|show_message), end_message
JS vanilla setInterval 1s, JJ:HH:MM:SS, s'arrête à 0

### H-10 · Before / After
Settings : heading+subheading, color_scheme
Blocks (max 3) : comparison : image_before+image_after+label_before+label_after
Comportement : slider drag horizontal via input[type=range] custom

### H-11 · Instagram feed
Settings : heading, color_scheme, username, columns (4|6|8, default 6)
Note : placeholder + lien app si non connectée (pas d'API directe)

### H-12 à H-18 : Rich text, Image with text, Multicolumn, Collection list, Video, Map, Contact form
Specs standard — se référer aux noms pour déduire les settings logiques.
Contact form : {% form 'contact' %}, validation HTML5, success state inline.

### C-01 · Collection (template)
Requirements Shopify obligatoires : faceted filtering (availability/price/type/vendor/options), tri 8 options, pagination cursor-based (paginate by 24)
Settings : products_per_page (12|24|36), columns_desktop (3|4), columns_mobile (1|2), filters_position (sidebar|top), show_filter_count, enable_sticky_filters, image_ratio, show_secondary_image
Layout sidebar : 260px desktop, drawer mobile via bouton "Filtrer"
Active filters : pills effaçables au-dessus de la grille

### P-01 · Product (template)
Requirements Shopify obligatoires : accelerated checkout, rich media (image/video/3D/YouTube/Vimeo), pickup availability, related+complementary products, selling plans, Shop Pay Installments
Blocks : title+vendor, price+badges+selling plan pricing, variant_picker (color swatches+size buttons), quantity_input (+/-), buy_buttons (ATC+dynamic checkout+pickup), description, collapsible_tab (×N), share, complementary_products
Sticky ATC : apparaît quand ATC principal hors viewport, affiche image+titre+prix+variant+bouton
Galerie : thumbnails verticaux desktop, carousel mobile, zoom inline ou lightbox, vidéo + 3D model-viewer

### CT-01 · Cart
Settings : cart_type (drawer|page, default drawer), show_order_note, show_shipping_calculator
Drawer : event cart:open via PubSub, trap focus, Escape ferme, scroll-lock
Line items : image+titre+variant+price+qty+remove
Free shipping progress bar (threshold configurable)
Subtotal + checkout + dynamic checkout buttons + cross-sell 1-3 produits

### S-01 · Search
Predictive : API /search/suggest.json, debounce 300ms
Affiche : produits (image+titre+prix) + collections + articles + pages
Template : résultats paginés, faceted filtering comme collection

